docstring.long_description: Get a specific id message id from a list of messages
docstring.short_description: Filter a list of can messages

parameters.name: message_id
parameters.description: the id of the messages to extract from the list of messages

parameters.name: messages
parameters.description: Stateful connection with a list of can.Message

returns.name: Stateful
returns.description: Stateful object with only the messages with the `message_id`
